Subject: [PATCH] drm/amdgpu: Add check to prevent IH overflow
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: e4180c4253f3f2da09047f5139959227f5cf1173
Patch-mainline: v5.12-rc1
